cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.AR 

This paper is about deep neural networks and their flexibility in numerical precision during inference. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also discusses the trade-off between accuracy and runtime efficiency, which falls under the sub-categories cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.AR (Hardware Architecture).
